Q_DESC:
Given two strings, find the longest common subsequence shared by the two.

Input Format

You will be given two strings on two lines.

Output Format

A single string which contains the longest common subsequence of characters in the two input strings.
TESTCASE_1:
AABBCC
ABCAB
###---###SEPERATOR---###---
The Longest Common Subsequence is AAB
TESTCASE_2:
abcde
aycze
###---###SEPERATOR---###---

The Longest Common Subsequence is ace
